@startuml
title Engine Runtime State Machine (Deterministic Lock + Identity/Status Gates)

' =========================
' DARK MODE REVIEW THEME
' =========================

skinparam backgroundColor #121417
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName JetBrains Mono
skinparam defaultFontColor #f3f5f7
skinparam linetype polyline

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #26313c
  BorderColor #7c8b9b
  FontColor #ffffff
  StartColor #79b8ff
  EndColor #79b8ff
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #2a3138
  BorderColor #8b98a6
  FontColor #f3f5f7
}

skinparam ArrowColor #79b8ff
skinparam ArrowFontColor #f3f5f7

state "PreValidation" as PreValidation
state "Identity + Status Check" as IdentityCheck
state "Validated" as Validated
state "Loading" as Loading
state "Initializing" as Initializing
state "Locked Runtime" as Locked
state "Abort" as Abort #4a2c2f
state "Shutdown" as Shutdown

[*] --> PreValidation : launch request

PreValidation -[#9de37e]-> IdentityCheck : load metadata + status + ownership snapshot + version tuple
IdentityCheck -[#9de37e]-> Validated : hash + ownership mapping + tuple + DAG pass\nstatus = active or deprecated
Validated -[#9de37e]-> Loading : deterministic load plan emitted
Loading -[#9de37e]-> Initializing : core_mod + ordered mods loaded
Initializing -[#9de37e]-> Locked : registration completed
Locked -[#9de37e]-> Shutdown : normal termination

PreValidation -[#c87878]-> Abort : metadata/manifest failure
IdentityCheck -[#c87878]-> Abort : banned/pending/quarantined/mapping mismatch
Validated -[#c87878]-> Abort : dependency conflict
Loading -[#c87878]-> Abort : symbol resolution failure
Initializing -[#c87878]-> Abort : registration failure
Abort -[#c87878]-> Shutdown : fail closed

Locked -[#79b8ff]-> Locked : deterministic tick loop

note right of IdentityCheck
Status policy:
- active: allow
- deprecated: warn + allow
- pending/review_required/banned/quarantined: reject
end note

note right of Locked
Runtime lock invariants:
- Mod graph is immutable after lock
- No runtime load/unload mutation
- Execution order remains deterministic
end note

@enduml
